snippet.title: Best VGM 711 - Deathsmiles IIX - Inside the White Darkness (Field E)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Arcade / Xbox 360
Deathsmiles IIX (2010)
Inside the White Darkness (Field E)
Manabu Namiki
